  "instructions": [
    "Heat 1 tablespoon of vegetable oil in a large wok over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the onion, carrots, and bell peppers to the wok and stir-fry for 3 minutes.",
    "Add the mushrooms to the wok and stir-fry for another 2 minutes.",
    "Add the rice vermicelli noodles to the wok and stir-fry for 2 minutes.",
    "Pour in the soy sauce and sesame oil, and stir-fry for 1 minute.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Transfer the noodles to a serving dish and serve immediately.",
